      "message": "is this going to be used for more than test results? If no, I would consider:\n\n   type TestResultsService struct {...}\n   LUCI_CONTEXT[\"test_results\"] \u003d {...}\n\n\"Sink\" took me a minute to parse, and \"resultsink\" seems pretty generic; Should the result of the recipe go there? What if the result of some process is a large amount of data?",
