      "writtenOn": "2019-11-06T02:30:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e I believe other ResultDB products will also use LUCI_CONTEXT in the future, is that correct?\n\nif they exist, yeah, but currently i cannot imagine anything that is not test-specific. Do you have examples? The only non-test results that we are considering is build artifacts. Those don\u0027t necessarily require such a sink. They can be uploaded by recipes by making ResultDB RPCs directly.",
